{% extends 'frontend_layout.html.twig' %}

{% block content %}
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card bg-dark text-white col-md-10 offset-md-1">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">
                    <a href="{{ path('frontend_static_page_how_to') }}">{{ 'How to'|trans }}</a> - {{ 'Rewards'|trans }}
                </h5>
                <div>
                    You can visit "Rewards" section by clicking <a href="{{ path('frontend_reward_index') }}"><i class="fas fa-award"></i> {{ 'Rewards'|trans }}</a> in navigation menu.
                </div>
                <br>
                <div>
                    Rewards are important part of this system. With rewards you can selfmotivate yourself.
                </div>
                <br>
                <div>
                    To add new Reward you need to click on <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"><i class="fas fa-pen-fancy"></i> {{ 'Create a reward'|trans }}</button>.
                    You need to provide reward title, type and required number of completions. You can assign reward to particular routine. You can also provide additional description.
                </div>
                <br>
                <div>
                    You can edit each reward created by yourself. You can change it's title, type, required number of completions and description.
                </div>
                <br>
                <div>
                    Now when you visit "Rewards" section by clicking <a href="{{ path('frontend_reward_index') }}"><i class="fas fa-award"></i> {{ 'Rewards'|trans }}</a> in navigation menu again you will see a list of your rewards.
                    You can view more details about each reward when you click <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> {{ 'Show'|trans }}</button> next to its name.
                </div>
                <br>
                <div>
                    Your next step could be creating a project. Please read more in <a href="{{ path('frontend_static_page_how_to_projects') }}">{{ 'Projects'|trans }}</a> documentation.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}

{% block title %}
    {{ parent() }} - {{ 'How to'|trans }} - {{ 'Rewards'|trans }}
{% endblock %}
